username requirements:
-should not starts with number or special char
-should have at least 3 char
__________________________________

email requirements:
-should not starts with @
-domain should match one of the following domains :
gmail.com
yahoo.com
hotmail.com
outlook.com
____________________________________

phone number requirements:
-should start with 01
-number length should not exceed 11
___________________________________

password requirements:
-password length at least 8 chars
-password should have at least one special char
-password should have at least one upper case char
-password should have mix of numbers and chars and special char